    <p>{`You can compile any controller to have the same method name if they have different parameter type or numbers. This is normal in .Net framework but what MVC developer must know is that you cannot have 2 actions (which are methods) with the same name even if they doesn't have the same parameter type. That mean you cannot have :`}</p>
