      }}>{` public ActionResult Edit(MyObjectToEdit obj) { //... } 
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`This will fail when you will call these because the MVC framework won't know which one to call. You have two solutions to make MVC routing know which action to use. First, you can change the name. I think it's obvious that if you have different name that the routing won't have any problem to know which one to choose.`}</p>
