      <li parentName="ul">{`Return sensitive information. This can be solved by using SSL.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Using Get with Json. This can be solved by using Post or having multiple name instead of having the same action with two types of Http call type.`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul">{`The browser support "`}<strong parentName="li">{`defineSetter`}</strong>{`" which is where the vulnerability is executed. this one, you have no control.`}</li>
